{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"File","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/File","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Konstruktor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/File\"><code>File()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/lastModified\"><code>lastModified</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/lastModifiedDate\"><code>lastModifiedDate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/File/name\"><code>name</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/File/type\"><code>type</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/webkitRelativePath\"><code>webkitRelativePath</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Das<strong><code>File</code></strong> Interface stellt Informationen über Dateien bereit und erlaubt den Zugriff auf deren Inhalt.</p>\n\n<p><code>File</code> werden generell von einem <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> Objekt&nbsp;als das Ergebnis einer Benutzerauswahl von Dateien über ein&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/Input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a></code>&nbsp;Element, von einem <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer\" title=\"DragDrop/DataTransfer\"><code>DataTransfer</code></a>&nbsp;Objekt eines&nbsp;Drag-and-Drop-Vorgangs,<span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;oder von der&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">mozGetAsFile()</code><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">&nbsp;API eines&nbsp;<a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a> zurückgegeben</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.5;\">. In Gecko ist es von privilegiertem Code aus möglich, den Konstruktor direkt mit einem String Pfad oder einem&nbsp;<code>nsIFile</code> aufzurufen. Siehe&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Extensions/Using_the_DOM_File_API_in_chrome_code\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Using the DOM File API in chrome code</a> für weitere Details.</span></p>\n\n<p>Die Dateireferenz kann nach der Formularübermittlung gespeichert werden, während der Benutzer über keine Internetverbindung verfügt. Somit können die Daten empfangen und hochgeladen werden, sobald die Internetverbindung wiederhergestellt ist.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Das<code>File</code> Interface erbt ebenso von dem <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> Interface.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"file.lastmodifieddate_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File/lastModifiedDate\"><code>File.lastModifiedDate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span> </dt>\n <dd>Das&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\">Date</a></code> der letzten Veränderung der Datei,&nbsp;referenziert durch das&nbsp;<code>File</code> Objekt.</dd>\n <dt id=\"file.name\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/File/name\"><code>File.name</code></a> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span> </dt>\n <dd>Der Name der Datei, referenziert durch das&nbsp;<code>File</code> Objekt.</dd>\n <dt id=\"file.filename\"><a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/API/File/name\"><code>File.fileName</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span> <span title=\"(Firefox 7.0 / Thunderbird 7.0 / SeaMonkey 2.4)\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit Gecko 7.0</span></dt>\n <dd>Der Name der Datei, referenziert durch das&nbsp;<code>File</code> Objekt.</dd>\n <dt id=\"file.filesize\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Blob/size\"><code>File.fileSize</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span> <span title=\"(Firefox 7.0 / Thunderbird 7.0 / SeaMonkey 2.4)\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit Gecko 7.0</span></dt>\n <dd>Die Größe der Datei in Bytes.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"method_overview","title":"Methods","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>The <code>File</code> interface also inherits methods from the <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> interface.</em></p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"file.getasbinary\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>File.getAsBinary()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"(Firefox 7.0 / Thunderbird 7.0 / SeaMonkey 2.4)\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit Gecko 7.0</span></dt>\n <dd>Returns a string containing the file's data in raw binary format.</dd>\n <dt id=\"file.getasdataurl\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>File.getAsDataURL()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"(Firefox 7.0 / Thunderbird 7.0 / SeaMonkey 2.4)\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit Gecko 7.0</span></dt>\n <dd>A string containing the file's data encoded as a <code>data:</code> URL.</dd>\n <dt id=\"file.getastextstring_encoding\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Die Beschreibung hierüber wurde bisher noch nicht geschrieben. Bitte überlege, mitzuwirken!\"><code>File.getAsText(string encoding)</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg> <span title=\"(Firefox 7.0 / Thunderbird 7.0 / SeaMonkey 2.4)\" class=\"notecard inline obsolete\">Veraltet seit Gecko 7.0</span></dt>\n <dd>Returns the file's contents as a string in which the file's data is interpreted as text using a given encoding.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Specifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"Die 'File API' Spezifikation\" rel=\" noopener\">File API</a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Arbeitsentwurf</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility_2","title":"Browser compatibility","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect2\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>13</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/3\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2008-06-17.\">3.0</a> (1.9) (non standard)<br>\n    <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/7\" title=\"Veröffentlicht am 2011-09-26.\">7</a> (7) (standard)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td>11.5</td>\n   <td>6.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Phone</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>25</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Nicht unterstützt</span></td>\n   <td>11.1</td>\n   <td>6.0</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Implementation notes","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"gecko_notes\">Gecko notes</h4>\n\n<ul>\n <li>In Gecko, you can use this API from chrome code. See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Extensions/Using_the_DOM_File_API_in_chrome_code\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Using the DOM File API in chrome code</a> for details.</li>\n <li>Starting in Gecko 6.0 (Firefox 6.0 / Thunderbird 6.0 / SeaMonkey 2.3), privileged code (such as extensions) can pass an <code>nsIFile</code> object to the DOM <code>File</code> constructor to specify the file to reference.</li>\n <li>Starting in Gecko 8.0 (Firefox 8.0 / Thunderbird 8.0 / SeaMonkey 2.5), you can use <code>new File</code> to create <code>File</code> objects from XPCOM component code instead of having to instantiate the <code>nsIDOMFile</code> object directly. The constructor takes, in contrast to Blob, as second argument the filename. The filename can be any String.\n  <pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">File File(\n&nbsp; Array parts,\n&nbsp; String filename,\n  BlobPropertyBag properties\n);</pre>\n </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"chrome_code_-_scope_availability","title":"Chrome Code - Scope Availability","isH3":false,"content":"<p>To use from chrome code, JSM and Bootstrap scope, you have to import it like this:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>Cu<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">importGlobalProperties</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'File'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p><code>URL</code> is available in Worker scopes.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_API/Using_files_from_web_applications\" title=\"Using files from web applications\">Using files from web applications</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Extensions/Using_the_DOM_File_API_in_chrome_code\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Using the DOM File API in chrome code</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Components.utils.importGlobalProperties\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Components.utils.importGlobalProperties</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Methods","id":"method_overview"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility_2"},{"text":"Chrome Code - Scope Availability","id":"chrome_code_-_scope_availability"},{"text":"See also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"DasFile Interface stellt Informationen über Dateien bereit und erlaubt den Zugriff auf deren Inhalt.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"File","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"File","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"File","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"File","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"File","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"File","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"File","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"File","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"File","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"File","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/file","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/file/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/File","title":"File"}],"pageTitle":"File - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}